{"tid":1567362,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中村屋壽司你今日幫襯左未","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:37:04.000Z","uid":320468,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"802dcb022977e16b989f2a4872edcdb71b058287","tid":1567362,"uid":320468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"長野縣地方報紙《信濃每日新聞》的記者來港，採訪了同為長野縣出身的在港日本人。<br />\n<br />\n相中的外賣壽司店是「中村屋Sushi Nakamuraya」。<br />\n<br />\n老闆中村先生表示，店舖的營業額自6月以來持續減少，日本人經營者當中存在對示威者不滿的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n然而，中村先生「希望尊重香港人的選擇，並為香港人打氣」。<br />\n<br />\n「中村屋Sushi Nakamuraya」堅持以空運新鮮食材製作正宗日本壽司，作為香港的一份子紮根香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sushinakamurahk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsushinakamurahk&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=fc7a6a05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sushinakamurahk</a><br />\n<br />\n良心小店，大家識做啦！<br />\n<br />\n手動轉<br />\n良心小店一定要多多支持<br />\n香港要搵到好食既日本野真係好難，尤其係日本人開既食店，好多時都好貴..難得有良心小店！"},{"pid":"b069afd6520fc193bd45e74a6825db4116c7256c","tid":1567362,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03ac4065418800b19067bd4f7f11038f85a44f8","tid":1567362,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb95272fb3a80650708f39cc3c7e37e9b14e1f6","tid":1567362,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://n